social_posts.post_text: Keep calm and look like Barbie! Check out my girls @skyebearz Doll House @thedollhouseps
Onto the next big thing

Happy Birthday to my baby Punica! 10 years I’ve had her! She became part of my personality! We moved and traveled to so many different places together! Lord knows if it wasn’t for her, I wouldn’t be here today! It didn’t matter what I went through she still needed me to feed and walk her and snap out of it. Shes always full of joy and happiness! Doesn’t matter if it was 5 mins or 8 hours she greets me with love and excitement every single time! There’s not a moment I get lonely with her cuddling me to sleep every single night! 🥰 my little buddy!

We are powerful when we come together! You all make me feel supported and loved! Im excited to see how everything unfolds it self in 2023!!! Happy holidays and merry Christmas to everyone! And a special thank you to @marialagios for always putting us together and plan everything! #girlspower
Merry Christmas! 🎁🎄
I’m grateful every day for having a circle of friends to help build each other up not only in our personal life but also in business! I love my team #dreamteam #career #ao

Falling in love with the process

HER! She’s a goddess walking with fire in her eyes! She had her fair shares of heart breaks and Trials, but never let them hinder her next success! She turns everything she touches into Gold! She fights for her friends and shows compassion! Her beauty is unmatched, her passion and momentum in business can not be found in another! I’m proud to call you my sister, my best friend and my business partner! As we grow closer! Words can’t describe how grateful I am to have you in my corner! I thank god every day that I have you by my side. I love you so much! HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU AGAIN @marialagios
R E F L E C T I O N

My Ying to my Yang! My lock to my key! We laugh, we cry and we build together! Lord knows how much I love you! I’m so freaking proud of the woman you’ve become! You are flourishing and blooming! I’m excited to unlock our new journey! Happy Birthday @leyna.love_ #newchapter
